模拟，类似 10 到 26 进制转换。

```python
class Solution:
    def convertToTitle(self, n: int) -> str:
        ans = ""
        while n > 0:
            t = n % 26
            n //= 26
            if t == 0:
                ans += 'Z'
                n -= 1
            else:
                ans += chr(ord('A') + t - 1)
        return ans[::-1]
```
